\begin{align*} \frac{15 yahs}{\frac{75}{8} bahs} &= \frac{1000 yahs}{x bahs}\\ 15x &= 1000 \cdot \frac{75}{8}\\ x &= 625. \end{align*}
Therefore, $625 bahs$ are equal in value to 1000 yahs.

